# DualRead browser extension — public env vars only.
#
# The extension currently has no build-time env dependencies. This file
# is a placeholder so contributors know where Phase 5+ vars will land
# (e.g. when the extension starts calling the FastAPI backend).
#
# Naming convention: anything Vite must inline at build time MUST be
# prefixed `VITE_` (it ends up in the shipped JS — never put a secret
# behind a VITE_* name). Server-only values do not belong in this repo.

# Phase 5 (Web client integration) — not yet wired.
# VITE_BACKEND_URL=https://api.dualread.local
